<div id="pf19" class="pf w0 h0" data-page-no="19"><div class="pc pc19 w0 h0"><div class="t m0 x9 h5 yb ff5 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls9 ws0">24 <span class="ff4 fs0 ls0">  北京大学汇丰商学院问答 </span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h6 y20 ff6 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y2a ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">语言宣说——说有也不对、说无也不对，不能用思维分别。<span class="_ _a"></span> </div><div class="t m0 x3e h13 yf6 ffe fs2 fc0 sc0 ls36 ws0">（三） <span class="_ _8"> </span><span class="fff ls1">问：<span class="ff4 fs3 ls3f">我是学会的学员，请上师对我们组的学</span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h13 yf7 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">员说几句祝福和鼓励的话。<span class="fff fs2"> </span></div><div class="t m0 x3e h3 yf8 fff fs2 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">答<span class="ffb">：</span></div><div class="t m0 x3f h4 yf9 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls20 ws0">希望大家通过修行，<span class="_ _10"></span>让此起彼伏的分别念停下来，</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yfa ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">进而遣除内心的无明和迷惑，<span class="_ _9"></span>认识到万法实相，<span class="_ _9"></span>之后利益一</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yfb ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">切众生！ </div><div class="t m0 x1b h4 yfc ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">成佛，不是为自己幸福，如果为了自己的幸福而修行，</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yfd ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls1b ws0">这没有太大意义。<span class="_ _7"></span>幸福是建立在利他基础上的，<span class="_ _7"></span>所以，<span class="_ _7"></span>我希</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yfe ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">望你们以实际行动利益众生。 </div><div class="t m0 x3e h13 yff ffe fs2 fc0 sc0 ls36 ws0">（四） <span class="_ _8"> </span><span class="fff ls1">问：<span class="ff4 fs3 ls3f">怎样才能做到“参禅不在腿，念佛不在</span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h13 y100 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">嘴”？<span class="fff fs2"> </span></div><div class="t m0 x3e h3 y101 fff fs2 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">答<span class="ffb">：</span></div><div class="t m0 x27 h4 y102 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">“参禅不在腿，<span class="_ _9"></span>念佛不在嘴”<span class="_ _b"></span>，<span class="_ _9"></span>这是从究竟上讲的。</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y103 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">但对初学者而言，参禅还是要盘起双腿，佛要一句一句念。</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y104 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">到了最高境界时，<span class="_ _9"></span>就可以不必执著这种形式，<span class="_ _9"></span>行住坐卧都可</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y105 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">以修行，<span class="_ _7"></span>比如正要发脾气时，<span class="_ _7"></span>立即反观自心，<span class="_ _7"></span>心就可以平静</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y106 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">下来。 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
